
	
The folder structure and the rules behind it is as followed...


=========================================================================================================

\play\[your_developer_name]\*

	- A place where you may store code related to (but not coupled to) the NGEN framework\components.

=========================================================================================================

\develop\*

        - A development copy of each major.minor[patch] of the framework sources.

        - Each patch required must have a new merge cut BEFORE development begins.  ie. \1.0\ -> \1.0a\

        - After development of a patch, create a .patch file and place in \patch\ folder.
        
        - A patch must only be applied to the latest major.minor.  Earlier minor versions lose support!
        
=========================================================================================================

\patch\*

        - A each patch created for the framework sources.  Using format: v1.0-to-v1.2a.patch

=========================================================================================================

\release\[platform]\*

        - Compiled binaries from each version of the framework sources for each supported platform.

=========================================================================================================

\design\*

        - Versioned\Unversioned content related to the DESIGN\MANAGMENT OF the NGEN framework.

=========================================================================================================

\media\*

        - Versioned\Unversioned content related to the USE OF the NGEN framework.
        - Content for tutorials\applications.

=========================================================================================================

	!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
									    
	  Do not remove, modify or commit into a folder not mentioned here. 
									    
	!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!